snippet.textDisplay: Well I think I’m done. They couldn’t even finish the Skywalker..er Palpatine trilogy correctly how is all of this going to work? I was a die hard fan that got the audio books/comics etc. I didn’t go to Rise Of Skywalker with my family cause of the Disney trilogy and how they treated fans(Remeber Rian Johnson mocking fans with “Your Snoke theory sucks” on Twitter?). I instead took my family of 6 to see Sonic(which I wasn’t interested in) only cause the director postponed the release date for the redesign and showed respect to the fans. I know SW fans are all over the map about what they want but I think if Lucas Film can stick to the Lore/world building instead of brining I’m whatever director who wants to write it will begin to get better. Lucas wasn’t a good writer or director but was great at creating characters and purpose for them, worlds, aliens races. Let’s get back to that. Mandolorian is the only thing I’m interested in but it won’t get me to get involved in anything else.
